#. <section class="sutta" id="sn37.15"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn37.15:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 37"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 37"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn37.15:0.2"
msgid "2. Dutiyapeyyālavagga"
msgstr "2. Abbreviated Texts"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 15. Akkodhanasutta → akodhano (pts1)
msgctxt "sn37.15:0.3"
msgid "15. Akkodhanasutta"
msgstr "15. Free of Anger"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn37.15:1.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho āyasmā anuruddho yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā … pe … "
"ekamantaṃ nisinno kho āyasmā anuruddho bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "Then Venerable Anuruddha went up to the Buddha … and said to him:"

msgctxt "sn37.15:1.2"
msgid ""
"“idhāhaṃ, bhante, mātugāmaṃ passāmi dibbena cakkhunā visuddhena "
"atikkantamānusakena kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā sugatiṃ saggaṃ lokaṃ "
"upapajjantaṃ."
msgstr ""
"“Sometimes, sir, with my clairvoyance that’s purified and superhuman, I see "
"that a female—when her body breaks up, after death—is reborn in a good "
"place, a heavenly realm."

msgctxt "sn37.15:1.3"
msgid ""
"Katīhi nu kho, bhante, dhammehi samannāgato mātugāmo kāyassa bhedā paraṃ "
"maraṇā sugatiṃ saggaṃ lokaṃ upapajjatī”ti?"
msgstr ""
"How many qualities do females have so that they’re reborn in a good place, a "
"heavenly realm?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi4.244"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn37.15:2.1"
msgid ""
"“Pañcahi kho, anuruddha, dhammehi samannāgato mātugāmo kāyassa bhedā paraṃ "
"maraṇā sugatiṃ saggaṃ lokaṃ upapajjati."
msgstr ""
"“Anuruddha, when females have five qualities, when their body breaks up, "
"after death, they are reborn in a good place, a heavenly realm."

msgctxt "sn37.15:2.2"
msgid "Katamehi pañcahi?"
msgstr "What five?"

#. VAR: akkodhano → akodhano (pts1)
msgctxt "sn37.15:2.3"
msgid ""
"Saddho ca hoti, hirimā ca hoti, ottappī ca hoti, akkodhano ca hoti, paññavā "
"ca hoti—"
msgstr "They’re faithful, conscientious, prudent, free of anger, and wise."

msgctxt "sn37.15:2.4"
msgid ""
"imehi kho, anuruddha, pañcahi dhammehi samannāgato mātugāmo kāyassa bhedā "
"paraṃ maraṇā sugatiṃ saggaṃ lokaṃ upapajjatī”ti."
msgstr ""
"When females have these five qualities, when their body breaks up, after "
"death, they are reborn in a good place, a heavenly realm.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn37.15:2.5"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
